1140
01:27:54,729 --> 01:27:57,106
One-Eyed Dragon, Date Masamune!

1141
01:27:57,190 --> 01:28:00,318
I will now fulfill the oath
we swore on the summit!

1142
01:28:00,401 --> 01:28:02,528
